title: Wiggle It - Ricki-Lee
description:
"Wiggle It" is a pop-R&B song by Australian singer Ricki-Lee, and the first single to be released from her forthcoming singles compilation. The single is scheduled for release on September 13, 2008 physically, and on September 16 digitally.

The song was co-written by urban artist & producer Israel Cruz. "Wiggle It" was written in 2006 for the album, "Brand New Day", but was not included due to Ricki-Lee stating that it did feel right on that mix of tracks. The track features a chorus sample from the 90&#039;s hit "Wiggle It" by 2 In A Room.

The video for Wiggle It was shot on Tuesday, August 19th at the Valve Nightclub in Melbourne. It is intended to be a parody of the typical club video, with Ricki-Lee looking for someone to spend her night with and coming up only with a number of characters who are all wrong for her. The video features a cameo by Big Brother &#039;06 contestant David Graham. The video premiered on Video Hits on Saturday, August 30th.
